The Sage 
	Character for Slay The Spire

A mechanic who studied about the cult of a blue bird.
She learned flying a carpet and brewing potions in order to stop its rise.

Starts with 40 HP, 169 gold	

Starting Relic:
	Flying Carpet
		Start each combat with 1 Flight. 

Starting Deck:
   4x Strike
		Attack, 1 Energy: 
		Deal 6 (9) damage.
	4x Defend
		Skill, 1 Energy: 
		Gain 5 (8) Block.
	1x Bold move
		Attack, 1 Energy:
		Deal 10 (13) damage. Gain 2 Frail.
	1x Fly
		Skill, 2 (1) Energy: 
		If you don't fly, gain 1 Flight.

15 Common Cards (grey)
	Pincer Repair
		Attack, 1 Energy
		Deal 9 (12) damage. The enemy gains 1 Artifact.
	Fire Brew
		Attack, 1 Energy: 
		Deal 6 (9) damage. Gain a Fire potion in 4 (3) turns.
	Salty Strike
		Attack, 1 Energy:
		Deal 6 (9) damage. The enemy gains 1 (2) Thirsty.
