Character-specific relics (Sage only)
	Byrd carpet
		Boss relic: 
		Replaces Flying carpet. Start each combat with 3 Flight. If you have 1 or 2 Flight at the start of your turn, set it to 3 again.
	Cook Book
		Common relic: 
		Start each combat with 1 Brewing.
	Ancient Magnet
		Uncommon relic: 
		Enemies have 1 less Strength per Artifact on them.
NEW:	Balloon Animal
		Uncommon relic:
		Draw 1 card at the start of your turn if you have no Flight.
	Can also use poison Relics (from Silent):
		- Snecko Skull
		- The Specimen
		- Twisted Funnel

Other relics (for all characters)
	Red Beast Statue
		Uncommon relic:
		Potions are 50% more likely to be uncommon or rare.
	Blowpipe
		Rare relic: 
		Whenever you throw a potion at an enemy, it also effects the other enemies.

Potions
	Flight Potion
		Rare, Sage only
		Gain 1 Flight.
	Fata Morgana
		Rare
		Apply 1 Disoriented.

Events
	Carpet trader
		Akt 2, for non-Sage characters
		Option 1: #rLose #r30% #rmax. #rHP. #gObtain #gthe #gFlying #gCarpet.
		Option 2: Leave
